Here’s my new poster for the @theavettbrothers show tonight in IL!
🦝
When I was younger I found this abandoned truck in the woods by my house in IL. I visit it each time I go back home. This barn is where my siblings and I would play hide and seek and jump off the hay bales. The Midwest has a lot of beauty, and I miss it often. 
🌽
These are 6 color silkscreens, I printed each color with lots transparent base. My AP copies will be on sale Sunday Aug 13 at 12noon EST
🏠
